title: #92Noon! A busy morning for the Vikings
description: Kirk's extension, CJ Ham gets a new deal and Anthony Harris is given the franchise tag. Breaking that down, plus a covenant catch-up with former Vikings asst Dline coach, now DLine coach at Arizona State, Robert Rodriguez chats with PA!
